<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/government-recruitment-service> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Government Recruitment Service (GRS) was launched in September 2017 and is part of the Cabinet Office’s Government People Group. GRS delivers award-winning recruitment services and functions for organisations across the Civil Service, supporting and enabling the recruitment of exceptional civil servants. GRS is part of the Government People Group ."@en .
